      "published": "2025-05-25T11:30:00Z",
      "content": "Great article, Sarah! I particularly appreciate your point about transparency vs. competition. We're seeing this tension play out in real-time with companies like OpenAI and Google. The challenge is that the incentive structures currently reward secrecy over openness. How do we change that?",
