      "type": "Note", 
      "id": "https://sarahstech.blog/comments/ai-ethics-reply-1",
      "published": "2025-05-25T12:15:00Z",
      "content": "@alexdev That's exactly the crux of it! I think we need regulatory frameworks that incentivize transparency without completely killing competitive advantage. Maybe something like mandatory algorithmic impact assessments for systems above certain thresholds, similar to environmental impact studies. What do you think about the EU's approach with the AI Act?",
