      "type": "Note",
      "id": "https://sarahstech.blog/comments/remote-work-comment-1",
      "published": "2025-05-20T15:45:00Z", 
      "content": "This hits so close to home. I've been remote for 3 years and definitely fell into the 'always on' trap. What finally helped me was physically closing my laptop at 6 PM and putting it in another room. Sounds simple but it was a game changer for creating that mental boundary.",
      "attributedTo": {
        "type": "Person",
        "id": "https://linkedin.com/in/mikejohnson", 
        "name": "Mike Johnson",
        "preferredUsername": "mikej",
        "summary": "Product Manager at RemoteFirst Inc"
      },
      "inReplyTo": "https://sarahstech.blog/posts/remote-work-productivity",
      "to": ["https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Public"]
    },
