      "type": "Note",
      "id": "https://sarahstech.blog/comments/remote-work-reply-1",
      "published": "2025-05-20T16:30:00Z",
      "content": "@mikej That's such a great tip! The physical ritual of 'closing work' is so important. I've started doing something similar - I have a specific playlist I play while shutting down for the day. It signals to my brain that work is over. These small rituals can have such a big psychological impact.",
      "attributedTo": {
        "type": "Person", 
