      "published": "2025-05-11T08:30:00Z",
      "content": "One thing that's helped me as a maintainer is being very explicit about what I will and won't do. I created a 'contribution guidelines' that includes emotional boundaries, not just technical ones. It's helped filter out some of the more demanding requests and set expectations upfront.",
      "attributedTo": {
